<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Orpheus" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Orpheus,</orth> the fabulous poet and musician: <bibl n="shak. luc 553" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 553</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tgv 3.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. III, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 5.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. V, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 3.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 III, 1, 3</bibl>. Alluded to, though not named: <bibl n="shak. tit 2.4.51" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 4, 51</bibl>.
